videos.description: Taevion Kinsey takes advantage of Florida's turnover and rises up for a two-handed slam at the other end for Marshall.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Marshall’s Kinsey rocks the rim with two-handed slam) 2019/11/29

videos.headline: Marshall's Kinsey rocks the rim with two-handed slam

videos.description: Mikel Beyers cuts through the Florida defense and takes the open lane to the hoop for a slam dunk a couple of minutes before halftime.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Beyers races to the hoop for Marshall jam) 2019/11/29

videos.headline: Beyers races to the hoop for Marshall jam

videos.description: Andrew Nembhard keeps his defender on his hip while making his way towards the hoop, he then passes the ball off to Scottie Lewis who finishes the jam.
videos.headline: Florida's Lewis hammers it home

videos.description: Florida guard Ques Glover scores 10 points in 12 minutes en route to a 14-point game to help the Gators to a second-half rally and a 73-67 win vs. Marshall.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Freshman Glover powers Gators to victory) 2019/11/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Freshman Glover powers Gators to victory
